-- NBC Says Olympics Opening Viewing Highest Ever for Non-U.S. Site
-- B y   D a n   H a r t
-- 2012-07-28T13:31:49Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-07-28/nbc-says-olympics-opening-viewing-highest-ever-for-non-u-s-site.html
Comcast Corp. (CMCSA) ’s NBC Universal said
its tape-delayed broadcast of last night’s Olympic Opening
Ceremony had the best overnight rating for a non-U.S. venue.  The 23 rating and 40 share surpassed that of the 2008
Beijing opening ceremony as well as the 1994 opening ceremony in
Lillehammer, Norway, the network said in an e-mailed statement.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Dan Hart at 
 dahart@bloomberg.net  